---
title: Easy Honey Chipotle Beef & Carrot Couscous with Avocado Salsa & Coriander
description: This meal is like a rainbow in a bowl. Rich chipotle-honey beef strips are perfectly paired with bright orange carrot couscous, vibrant green avocado, fresh and fragrant red tomatoes and zesty yellow lemons! We’re eating all the colours tonight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
